Hare Krishna,

Please follow the following steps to use this project.

1. Open data.js
2. Add your email, password
3. Add link of groups you want to post in place of sample group links. Note the account should have permission to post in those groups.
4. Write your post in place of sample post written.
5. Install NodeJS
    If nodejs is installed in your computer than you can skip this step
    otherwise you can install nodejs from here 
    Windows - https://phoenixnap.com/kb/install-node-js-npm-on-windows
    Linux - https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/installation-of-node-js-on-linux/
    Mac - https://nodesource.com/blog/installing-nodejs-tutorial-mac-os-x/

    You can check if everything is installed by typing
    node -v
    npm -v
    in command line. this will give version of node and npm installed.
6. Open command prompt and go to folder location
7. type 'npm install' and press enter
8. type 'node index.js'
9. All done.. Sit back and watch code spreading your post.

In case of any issue feel free to contact.

